OL,5, The financial regulator says an        
OL,6, overhaul of its rules will tackle some 
OL,7, of the biggest frustrations held by    
OL,8, consumers.                             
OL,10,FUnder the new Consumer Duty, it should 
OL,11,Ftake customers no longer to make a     
OL,12,Fcomplaint than to be sold a product.   
OL,14,FThe Financial Conduct Authority (FCA)  
OL,15,Fis updating its rules on the treatment 
OL,16,Fof customers to focus on clarity and   
OL,17,Fvalue.                                 
OL,19,FIt said that should include ending long
OL,20,Fwaits on the phone or rip-off fees.    
